akka.stream.impl

Class SubFusingActorMaterializerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.stream.Materializer
      • akka.stream.impl.SubFusingActorMaterializerImpl

  • public class SubFusingActorMaterializerImpl
extends Materializer
    This materializer replaces the default phase with one that will fuse stages into an existing interpreter (via registerShell), rather than start a new actor for each of them.

    The default phases are left in-tact since we still respect .async and other tags that were marked within a sub-fused graph.
